    <div class="prose">
      <p>Sending a professional estimate used to mean opening Excel, manually typing line items, calculating material quantities, and hoping you didn't forget overhead. TradeQuote Pro replaces that workflow with custom templates, live material pricing, and one-click client delivery — turning a 45-minute task into a 5-minute process.</p>

      <p>This guide walks through every feature of TradeQuote Pro, from setup to sending your first estimate. By the end, you will know exactly how to use the tool to win more bids and save hours every week.</p>

      <h2>What TradeQuote Pro Does</h2>
      <p>TradeQuote Pro is a <strong>construction estimating and quoting platform</strong> purpose-built for home-service and B2B trades. It replaces spreadsheets, handwritten quotes, and back-and-forth emails with a centralized system that handles the math, formatting, and delivery of professional estimates.</p>

